Use the standard library
This is how to generate_integers of a and b:
   Remember that start is min of a and b
   Remember that stop is max of a and b
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that i is start

   Do this (sum of (diff of stop and start) and 1) times:
      When remainder of i and 2 is 0, then:
         Add result to i
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   The answer is result
Now you know